> Lamia moved close to Maurader and she waited for Maurader's command

Marauder looked down to see Lamia as she finally came out into the
open. "We go!" he said as his powerful wings beat to push him further
into the skies, his large heads looked around the scan the horizons.
"Unicron has declared this planet for himself, and so we will make
that happen." marauder's heads said in unison. One head glanced back
at the Maximal base, "and they will be too late to stop us."

Marauder glanced at Lamia, "and you my dear have much to do, for we
need all of our brethren."

With a laugh Marauder continued higher into the skies, away from the
Maximal base, and away into the distance.

OOC: I am not sure if Lamia can fly. If she cannot, please assume that
Marauder has picked her up and he carrying her if that is okay.

Preston
(Marauder)
